<paragraph blockId="24.[151,1436,1733,2010]" pageId="24" pageNumber="225">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,314,1841,1866]" pageId="24" pageNumber="225">Diagnosis</emphasis>
. The females of 
<taxonomicName box="[508,674,1841,1866]" class="Arachnida" family="Anyphaenidae" genus="Xiruana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="24" pageNumber="225" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cocha" status="n. sp.">
