<figureCitation captionStart="FIGURE 14" captionStartId="25.[151,250,1751,1773]" captionTargetBox="[151,1435,652,1709]" captionTargetId="figure@25.[151,1435,652,1710]" captionTargetPageId="25" captionText="FIGURE 14. Xiruana tribarrense n. sp.: A female epigynum, ventral view; B same, dorsal view. Xiruana cocha n. sp.: C female epigynum, ventral view; D same, dorsal view. Scale bars: B, D 0.25 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/242243/files/figure.png" pageId="24" pageNumber="225">
